item.title: CVE-2016-6553|2024-08-06T01:36:28.498Z -- nuuo -- nt-4040%20titan
item.description: Nuuo NT-4040 Titan, firmware NT-4040_01.07.0000.0015_1120, uses non-random default credentials of: admin:admin and localdisplay:111111. A remote network attacker can gain privileged access to a vulnerable device.
